response.overview: Highlights from the 1990-1991 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry. 'This is the hat trick!'. ROCK' EM SOCK' EM III tops off the three best selling hockey tapes of all time. Blue and I got together and came up with some new stuff: the All Cherry Team, out Pet Peeves, and of course, the best goals, saves and the hardest hits. Also, back by popular demand, more Coach's Corner highlights.  If you liked ROCK' EM SOCK' EM I & II, you'll love ROCK' EM SOCK' EM III. It's the best!
response.title: Don Cherry's Rock 'em Sock 'em Hockey 3
